with 
<taxonomicName authority="(Gray, 1835)" baseAuthorityName="Gray" baseAuthorityYear="1835" box="[208,573,1241,1268]" class="Insecta" family="Pseudophasmatidae" genus="Isagoras" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phasmida" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rugicollis">
<emphasis box="[208,420,1241,1267]" italics="true" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">Isagoras rugicollis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Gray, G. R." box="[435,565,1241,1268]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" refId="ref93213" refString="Gray, G. R. (1835) Synopsis of the species of insects belonging to the family of Phasmidae. Longman, Rees, Orme, Brown, Green and Longman, London, 48 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8697" type="book" year="1835">Gray, 1835</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. A detailed explanation is given above, in the comments for the genus.
</paragraph>
